Third-party components
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- PyMuPDF (pymupdf) .......... GNU AGPL-3.0 — PDF text/character extraction
- spaCy ...................... MIT — tokenization + NLP passes
- eyecite .................... BSD-2-Clause — legal citation extraction
- reporters-db / courts-db ... BSD-2-Clause — reporter + court metadata
- pydantic ................... MIT — schema validation
- typer ...................... MIT — CLI
- python-docx ................ MIT — DOCX emit
- pandas / matplotlib ........ BSD / PSF-compatible — audit artifacts

Sample documents shipped under `samples/` are public-domain U.S. federal
government edicts and synthetic content; see `samples/PROVENANCE.md`.
